        </ul>

        <h2>9. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>To the maximum extent permitted by applicable law, FemRes is not liable for:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Losses from use or inability to use services</li>
          <li>Damages from third-party content or links</li>
          <li>Data loss or system failures</li>
          <li>Indirect, special, or consequential damages</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>10. Service Modification and Termination</h2>
        <p>We reserve the right to modify, suspend, or terminate services at any time. We will try to provide advance notice for significant changes.</p>

        <h2>11. Dispute Resolution</h2>
        <p>In case of disputes:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>We encourage resolution through friendly negotiation</li>
          <li>If needed, resolution through online mediation platforms</li>
          <li>Serious disputes will be resolved according to applicable law</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>12. Terms Modification</h2>
        <p>We may update these Terms of Use. For significant changes, we will:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Post notices on the website</li>
          <li>Notify registered users via email</li>
          <li>Provide a reasonable transition period</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>13. Contact Information</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about these Terms of Use, please contact us:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Email: legal@femres.org</li>
          <li>GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/kantegger/femhub/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Submit an Issue</a></li>
        </ul>

        <div class="mt-12 p-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-50 to-pink-50 dark:from-purple-900/20 dark:to-pink-900/20 rounded-xl">
          <h3 class="text-purple-800 dark:text-purple-200 mt-0">Our Mission</h3>
          <p class="text-purple-700 dark:text-purple-300 mb-0">
            FemRes is committed to creating a safe, inclusive, and diverse feminist learning environment. We believe that through knowledge sharing and rational discussion, we can advance the cause of gender equality. Thank you for being part of this community!
